Titolo: Pixelus

Anno: 2004

Descrizione: Pixelus is a puzzle video game released for the Microsoft Windows and Mac OS X in 2005.  A deluxe version was released later in the year. The story follows a young Greek man named Claudius who is shipwrecked and rebuilds temple mosaics in order to gain the favor of the gods. The gameplay of Pixelus is a clone of the Japanese 2001 game Guru Logi Champ published for the Game Boy Advance.